message.content:
Breakfast:
- 1 cup of whole grain oats cooked with water or milk and topped with berries, sliced almonds, and a drizzle of honey.

Lunch:
- A salad made with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber slices, grilled chicken breast, and a light vinaigrette dressing. Serve with 1/2 cup of quinoa on the side.

Snack:
- A medium apple with 1 tablespoon of natural peanut butter.

Dinner:
- Grilled salmon with lemon and herbs, served with roasted vegetable medley (broccoli, carrots, zucchini, and red bell pepper) and a side of brown rice.

Don't forget to stay hydrated throughout the day by drinking plenty of water!
